# eSchool Market Place non functional requirements

### Scalability
 system should be able to scale to accomodate load during peak time

### Availability
1. System should be available 99.99% of time
2. Failover mechanishm should ensure high availability in case of failure


### Reliability
1. System should perform adequately/consistently

### Maintainability
1. Should follow best practices
2. Regular code reviews
3. Automated testing

### Usability 
1. User should find the system easy to use

### Performant
1. System should perform good 



